<section class="content-section reveal">
  <h2>How to Use This Calculator</h2>

  <p>Enter your <strong>bill amount</strong> and select a <strong>tip percentage</strong>. The calculator instantly shows your tip amount and total. The default is 18% — the most common tip in the US.</p>

  <p>Splitting with a group? Expand <strong>"More Options"</strong> to enter the <strong>number of people</strong>. The calculator divides the total evenly and shows each person's share — tip included.</p>

  <h3>Share your result</h3>
  <p>Every input is encoded in the URL. Click <strong>Share</strong>, send the link to your group — they'll see the exact split. No re-entering, no screenshots.</p>
</section>

<!-- ── FORMULA ── -->
<section class="content-section reveal">
  <h2>The Formula</h2>
  <p>Tip calculation uses two straightforward formulas:</p>
  <div class="formula-box">
    Tip = Bill &times; Percentage &divide; 100
  </div>
  <div class="formula-box">
    Per Person = (Bill + Tip) &divide; Number of People
  </div>
  <p>Where:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Bill</strong> = the pre-tip total on your check</li>
    <li><strong>Percentage</strong> = the tip rate you choose (e.g. 15, 18, 20, 25)</li>
    <li><strong>Number of People</strong> = how many are splitting the bill (default 1)</li>
  </ul>
</section>

